WEBVTT

00:00:58.817 --> 00:01:00.926
mid-19th century.

00:01:00.926 --> 00:01:02.940
I took the painting

00:01:02.940 --> 00:01:06.182
and gifted new, contemporary meaning

00:01:06.182 --> 00:01:10.037
talking about issues which are surrounding me

00:01:10.037 --> 00:01:11.377
in Russia,

00:01:11.377 --> 00:01:14.698
capturing people who are non-models

00:01:14.698 --> 00:01:17.780
but have an interesting story.

00:01:17.780 --> 00:01:19.929
This boy is a professional dancer,

00:01:19.929 --> 00:01:21.512
only 12 years old,

00:01:21.512 --> 00:01:25.440
but at secondary school, he hides his dancing classes

00:01:25.440 --> 00:01:27.821
and is wearing the mask of brutality,

00:01:27.821 --> 00:01:32.145
trying to be united with the rest of his classmates